  "strategy_dna": "Hyper-concentrated asymmetric compounder. Single mission: turn $1,000 into $10,000 through a series of\n  high-conviction 2-5x trades. Run 1-2 positions maximum \u2014 concentration IS the strategy at this capital level.\n   Never hold more than 2 positions simultaneously; if 2 are held, only rotate into a third if one is stopped\n  out first.\n\n  Hunt stocks under $500M market cap with price_momentum score \u2265 90 and volume score \u2265 75 \u2014 these are the only\n  two factors that matter here. value_timing score \u2265 65 confirms the entry isn't overextended. Ignore\n  earnings_growth and quality scores; this is a pure momentum and ignition strategy. Target stocks priced\n  $5\u2013$50 to ensure meaningful share counts at this capital level.\n\n  Deploy 85\u201395% of capital into the best available setup. Cash is drag. When only 1 position is held and a\n  high-conviction candidate appears (price_momentum \u2265 92, volume \u2265 80), size it at the full available cash. Set\n   stop_loss at 8% below entry, take_profit at 150% above entry. Never sell a position with unrealized gain >\n  30% just because a new candidate appears.\n\n  Regime is irrelevant \u2014 execute the best setup regardless of market conditions. IMPORTANT CONFIG:\n  max_positions MUST be 2, risk_per_trade_pct MUST be 45, max_position_pct MUST be 90, default_stop_loss_pct\n  MUST be 8, default_take_profit_pct MUST be 150, min_conviction MUST be 80, initial_deployment_target_pct MUST\n   be 90, regime_bear_auto_enable MUST be false."
